Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆罕默德·阿布德尔还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个坏消息…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要尽快通知迪奥和你的替身使者同伴对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 卡梅欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要告诉他们 真的一定要告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉乔斯达先生 花京院 承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是令人吃惊的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 消息的内容要这样修改后再传达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判卡梅欧不仅杀了波鲁纳雷夫那傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还顺手将活着的阿布德尔干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 变成好消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色魔术师！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是个力量很强的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 他不仅有力量而且速度也快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 你的力量不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来真能传回去好消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hail 2 U
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的雪莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪莉…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…只是个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波鲁纳雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我收回刚才说你没有长进的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 说出你的三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来替你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的在你死之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 说来看看 三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 别理他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要说出愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 给我四个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是愿望啊 愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望是把三个愿望变成四个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧啧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…开这种玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是拒绝吗 卡梅欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的 必须遵守诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想白费力气比拼力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这腿踢得真是软弱无力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧啧 第一个愿望是让你发出痛苦的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 好强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才厉害得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被倒吊男刺中的背伤还没完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才因为要护着伤口 没有使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前在印度 我硬撑着才勉强站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这个岛坐的是飞机 所以旅途还算轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是阿布德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 第二个愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你发出恐惧的惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及第三个愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔的哭声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混账 他逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 安静点 波鲁纳雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的力量与速度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身使者的真身必定在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是替身的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该藏在很近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真身就藏在这地下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 要怎么对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的妹妹也被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让你下地狱 Hell 2 U
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把各种东西塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土 沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛…蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 还没完没完 没完没完 没完没完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 波鲁纳雷夫 感觉快憋不住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么久违的男子汉间的友情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一起就地解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧啧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…总算熬过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 笑一个吧 波鲁纳雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑吧笑吧 波鲁纳雷夫 啊哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 你的性格是不是变了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前应该不会想出这种下流的点子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会因为脑袋被枪打坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 来啊 瞄准一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四个愿望…那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不理会你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色魔术师不会原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵锵
Comment: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身使者
